cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict user intent based on search queries. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques. Finally, since the paper deals with predicting user behavior, it may also fall under the sub-category of computer security (cs.CR).
